{"tid":2014432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【諗縮數？】JM疫情下有工開賺大錢 照炒效力十幾年助手","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T04:44:03.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"72a20dec093d0ff3934e2363b28b52a884cdc8ed","tid":2014432,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXT6qAv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXT6qAv.png&h=9e82ea5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n31歲文詠珊（Janice Man）最近復工拍新電影版《倚天屠龍記》飾演趙敏，穩袋900萬元片酬，開工前即爆出是非。據知幫JM打工十幾年的助手阿霖人緣好，以前幫衛蘭打工時，對衛蘭一切照顧有加，為人夠細心，黎明都好滿意，JM離開公司後，主動邀他一齊過檔，怎料在今次疫情下，疑有人覺得助手白攞人工，見諗縮數無效，即補一個月人工即炒阿霖，可憐阿霖多年來一直陪在她身邊打江山，卻頓時加入疫下失業大軍。許多圈中人得知他慘食無情雞，均替他不值，消息已在圈中廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200511/4C7ZZKEIMYW4Q7WN6GWH6GYTFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200511%2F4C7ZZKEIMYW4Q7WN6GWH6GYTFQ%2F&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=e812bfab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200511%2F4C7ZZKEIMYW4Q7WN6GWH6GYTFQ%2F&h=bd2f4ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200511/4C7ZZKEIMYW4Q7WN6GWH6GYTFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"da4b529c07c87c280fb7cc06a09ae6ffb6d3c343","tid":2014432,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/RBvym_nAPRUk55Avcvdh8FHqmyA=/393x221/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/WNOT3CWRY3SYTDRRJ4VX6OJZ7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FRBvym_nAPRUk55Avcvdh8FHqmyA%3D%2F393x221%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FWNOT3CWRY3SYTDRRJ4VX6OJZ7U.jpg&h=d1cd8c